<div type="content"><ab facs="#facs_77_r1l2"><expan>L<ex>ieben</ex></expan> <expan>fr<ex>ewnde</ex></expan> / als wır nehſt auf des edeln <expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren</expan> <expan>H<ex>er</ex>n</expan> <expan>Heinr<ex>ich</ex></expan> <expan>Reẅſſe<ex>n</ex></expan> von </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_77_r1l3">Plawen / des <expan>elt<ex>er</ex>n</expan> <expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren</expan> ʒu Greẅcʒ / ſchrıft vnd <expan>begeru<ex>n</ex>g</expan> dıe er an </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_77_r1l4">eẅch vnd Jr vns fürbas getan habt / <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> <expan>dıen<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>Burkart<ex>en</ex></expan> Reıkarcʒ = </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_77_r1l5"><expan>hof<ex>er</ex></expan> ʒu <expan>eẅr<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>weıſh<ex>eit</ex></expan> gen Eger geſant <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> / <expan>Derſ<ex>elb</ex></expan> <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>dıen<ex>er</ex></expan> hat </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_77_r1l6">vns / wol geſagt vvıe Jm <expan>deſſ<ex>elben</ex></expan> <expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren</expan> von Plawen <expan>meynu<ex>n</ex>g</expan> daſelbs </ab>
