<ab facs="#facs_77_r1l9"><expan>dank<ex>en</ex></expan> wır <expan>eẅr<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>freẅntſ<ex>chaft</ex></expan> mıt <expan>gancʒe<ex>m</ex></expan> fleıſſ / Vnd <expan>laſſ<ex>en</ex></expan> eẅr <expan>erſamk<ex>eit</ex></expan> </ab>
